  "author": "Priya",
  "content": "<p>&nbsp;</p><h1 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: x-large;\">Cancellation &amp; Refund Policy</span></h1><div class=\"relative basis-auto flex-col -mb-(--composer-overlap-px) pb-(--composer-overlap-px) [--composer-overlap-px:28px] grow flex\"><div class=\"flex flex-col text-sm\"><section class=\"text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto [content-visibility:auto] supports-[content-visibility:auto]:[contain-intrinsic-size:auto_100lvh] R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]\" data-scroll-anchor=\"false\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-210\" data-turn-id=\"request-6963ed90-eee8-8322-87c1-9cb9c2c8f2b3-0\" data-turn=\"assistant\" dir=\"auto\"><div class=\"text-base my-auto mx-auto pb-10 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)\"><div class=\"[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn\"><div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow\"><div class=\"min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"ffe8f124-5065-46c2-ac00-e1da0042773b\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-5\" data-turn-start-message=\"true\" dir=\"auto\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden\"><div class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span>Welcome to <span data-end=\"62\" data-start=\"43\">Interview Preps</span>. By purchasing any digital product, PDF, notes, tutorials, or learning material from our website, you agree to the following Cancellation and Refund Policy.</span></span></div><hr data-end=\"224\" data-start=\"221\" /><h2 data-end=\"251\" data-section-id=\"jm1dsk\" data-start=\"226\">Digital Product Policy</h2><p data-end=\"411\" data-start=\"253\">All products available on this website are digital products delivered electronically through email, download links, or online access after successful payment.</p><p data-end=\"530\" data-start=\"413\">Because digital products cannot be returned once accessed or delivered, all purchases are generally considered final.</p><hr data-end=\"535\" data-start=\"532\" /><h2 data-end=\"559\" data-section-id=\"v98p02\" data-start=\"537\">Cancellation Policy</h2><p data-end=\"696\" data-start=\"561\">Orders can only be cancelled before the digital product is delivered or shared with the registered email address provided by the buyer.</p><p data-end=\"703\" data-start=\"698\">Once:</p><ul data-end=\"794\" data-start=\"704\"><li data-end=\"714\" data-section-id=\"11lo0rz\" data-start=\"704\">the PDF,</li><li data-end=\"731\" data-section-id=\"ad6u0g\" data-start=\"715\">download link,</li><li data-end=\"748\" data-section-id=\"puwgot\" data-start=\"732\">digital notes,</li><li data-end=\"767\" data-section-id=\"5dwgoc\" data-start=\"749\">tutorial access,</li><li data-end=\"794\" data-section-id=\"4pucf9\" data-start=\"768\">or any purchased content</li></ul><p data-end=\"873\" data-start=\"796\">has been sent or made accessible, cancellation requests will not be accepted.</p><hr data-end=\"878\" data-start=\"875\" /><h2 data-end=\"896\" data-section-id=\"1us7a8b\" data-start=\"880\">Refund Policy</h2><p data-end=\"948\" data-start=\"898\">Refunds are not applicable in the following cases:</p><ul data-end=\"1237\" data-start=\"950\"><li data-end=\"987\" data-section-id=\"1hew2lj\" data-start=\"950\">Incorrect email entered by the user</li><li data-end=\"1019\" data-section-id=\"sarapy\" data-start=\"988\">Change of mind after purchase</li><li data-end=\"1050\" data-section-id=\"8wqq5u\" data-start=\"1020\">Lack of device compatibility</li><li data-end=\"1097\" data-section-id=\"cssh3n\" data-start=\"1051\">Failure to read product description properly</li><li data-end=\"1160\" data-section-id=\"1vvb2e6\" data-start=\"1098\">Download issues caused by customer internet/network problems</li><li data-end=\"1183\" data-section-id=\"1ine6ge\" data-start=\"1161\">Accidental purchases</li><li data-end=\"1237\" data-section-id=\"wzdev8\" data-start=\"1184\">Delayed access caused by temporary technical issues</li></ul><hr data-end=\"1242\" data-start=\"1239\" /><h2 data-end=\"1268\" data-section-id=\"ddvwsp\" data-start=\"1244\">Eligible Refund Cases</h2><p data-end=\"1305\" data-start=\"1270\">A refund may be considered only if:</p><ul data-end=\"1495\" data-start=\"1307\"><li data-end=\"1362\" data-section-id=\"cssymm\" data-start=\"1307\">Payment is deducted multiple times for the same order</li><li data-end=\"1436\" data-section-id=\"1aetm2c\" data-start=\"1363\">Customer is charged, but product delivery completely fails from our side</li><li data-end=\"1495\" data-section-id=\"ibjck5\" data-start=\"1437\">Technical issues prevent delivery for an extended period</li></ul><p data-end=\"1568\" data-start=\"1497\">In such cases, users must contact us within <strong data-end=\"1551\" data-start=\"1541\">3 days</strong> of payment with:</p><ul data-end=\"1643\" data-start=\"1569\"><li data-end=\"1589\" data-section-id=\"6b153y\" data-start=\"1569\">Payment screenshot</li><li data-end=\"1616\" data-section-id=\"23nyyi\" data-start=\"1590\">Registered email address</li><li data-end=\"1643\" data-section-id=\"lnj0g5\" data-start=\"1617\">Transaction/reference ID</li></ul><p data-end=\"1728\" data-start=\"1645\">After verification, eligible refunds may be processed within <strong data-end=\"1727\" data-start=\"1706\">5?7 business days</strong>.</p><hr data-end=\"1733\" data-start=\"1730\" /><h2 data-end=\"1753\" data-section-id=\"jvh3rv\" data-start=\"1735\">Processing Time</h2><p data-end=\"1797\" data-start=\"1755\">Approved refunds, if applicable, may take:</p><ul data-end=\"1906\" data-start=\"1798\"><li data-end=\"1839\" data-section-id=\"1xjj8ak\" data-start=\"1798\">5?7 business days for UPI/bank accounts</li><li data-end=\"1906\" data-section-id=\"8ldaa8\" data-start=\"1840\">Additional time depending on the payment provider or bank processing</li></ul><hr data-end=\"1911\" data-start=\"1908\" /><h2 data-end=\"1935\" data-section-id=\"d0jpe1\" data-start=\"1913\"><br /></h2></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div>"
